<% content_for :title, "<%= app_name %>" %>

<main class="dare-home">
  <h1><%= app_name %></h1>
  <p>
    Rails 8 full-stack application scaffolded with the DARE method.
    Controllers render server-side views; business logic stays in
    <code>app/services/</code> and data access in <code>app/repositories/</code>.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Edit this page at <code>app/views/home/index.html.erb</code></li>
    <li>API docs (rswag): <code>/api-docs</code></li>
    <li>DARE metrics: <code>bundle exec rake dare:metrics</code></li>
  </ul>
</main>
